  "remarks": "Alexander Ustinov is a General Director of the Russian military industry company JSC Machine-Building Plant Arsenal. The company is a subject of Russian state defence orders and is engaged in the production of Lotos reconnaissance satellites and AK-176M naval guns. Lotos is used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine for target identification and AK-176M naval guns are installed in the Russian Navy ships that shell Ukrainian troops.",
